  "short_description": "SynthetiCell BioClicker is an Idle incremental simulator where you bring to life a colony of synthetic automaton cells. Inspired by the classic 'Game of Life' by mathematician John Horton Conway (1970) about the evolution of an organism. Can you guide your colony to prosperity?",
