  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage resources, create life and ensure the survival of a colony of thousands of synthetic cells in this fascinating incremental simulation game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the 'Game Of Life' by the illustrious mathematician John Horton Conway, where cells live or die according to 4 basic rules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This Idle revolution challenges you as a player to achieve a stable and prosperous ecosystem to ensure the species or else you will succumb to the challenges of evolution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/96e9a39796d18764d5b651acc207402a.avif?t=1745050479\" width=800 height=198 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Click equals life:</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As long as the environmental conditions are optimal. Watch how your colony grows and expands, but don't relax and improve your resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/456e8fe7675a47c050464a40a00c07d5.avif?t=1745050479\" width=800 height=254 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Nature is cruel:</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be careful! Also like in every living organism, malignant cells are generated that try to clone themselves and spread to destroy the colony. Progress in your defense skills as quickly as possible to face them and ensure the species.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/acb5661a7ab30722413c3c69df56989f.poster.avif?t=1745050479\" width=800 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/acb5661a7ab30722413c3c69df56989f.webm?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/acb5661a7ab30722413c3c69df56989f.mp4?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Bio-Mine or die:</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you don't get the essential elements the colony will die! Step inside a multicellular organism to explore and collect molecules essential for the formation of chemical bonds, without which life would not be possible. Upgrade the Nano-Bot-Cell molecule harvester and immune defense system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Sometimes having resources isn't everything!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Having to perfectly combine a long sequence of chemical elements is not easy to memorize or reproduce, but necessary for the prosperity of the colony.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Bonus events:</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get more extra 'coins' to increase your skills with random mini-games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>SynthetiCell BioClicker demonstrates how simple systems can generate surprising complexity, inspiring new research and applications in many fields.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/5f9f42a22519a319e4b580700d2a6f93.poster.avif?t=1745050479\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/5f9f42a22519a319e4b580700d2a6f93.webm?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/5f9f42a22519a319e4b580700d2a6f93.mp4?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>REAL examples of incredible patterns and shapes with the 'John Horton Conway' rules.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/003465bddb450c93cad5b6a386e3b9ee.apng?t=1745050479\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/003465bddb450c93cad5b6a386e3b9ee.poster.avif?t=1745050479\" class=\"bb_img\" width=89 height=145 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/838a5cc66e0456d2c55991b92c649846.apng?t=1745050479\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/838a5cc66e0456d2c55991b92c649846.poster.avif?t=1745050479\" class=\"bb_img\" width=137 height=137 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/07f46d51da004c22357b07393593f46a.apng?t=1745050479\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/07f46d51da004c22357b07393593f46a.poster.avif?t=1745050479\" class=\"bb_img\" width=98 height=98 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/661f815ca07c5c48d8508424e5e63dcc.poster.avif?t=1745050479\" width=126 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/661f815ca07c5c48d8508424e5e63dcc.webm?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/661f815ca07c5c48d8508424e5e63dcc.mp4?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/8267036dcf6ae3d5150a797592720639.poster.avif?t=1745050479\" width=84 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/8267036dcf6ae3d5150a797592720639.webm?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/8267036dcf6ae3d5150a797592720639.mp4?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join this Biosynthetic experience and discover a world where every click matters!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage resources, create life and ensure the survival of a colony of thousands of synthetic cells in this fascinating incremental simulation game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the 'Game Of Life' by the illustrious mathematician John Horton Conway, where cells live or die according to 4 basic rules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This Idle revolution challenges you as a player to achieve a stable and prosperous ecosystem to ensure the species or else you will succumb to the challenges of evolution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/96e9a39796d18764d5b651acc207402a.avif?t=1745050479\" width=800 height=198 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Click equals life:</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As long as the environmental conditions are optimal. Watch how your colony grows and expands, but don't relax and improve your resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/456e8fe7675a47c050464a40a00c07d5.avif?t=1745050479\" width=800 height=254 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Nature is cruel:</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be careful! Also like in every living organism, malignant cells are generated that try to clone themselves and spread to destroy the colony. Progress in your defense skills as quickly as possible to face them and ensure the species.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/acb5661a7ab30722413c3c69df56989f.poster.avif?t=1745050479\" width=800 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/acb5661a7ab30722413c3c69df56989f.webm?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/acb5661a7ab30722413c3c69df56989f.mp4?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Bio-Mine or die:</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you don't get the essential elements the colony will die! Step inside a multicellular organism to explore and collect molecules essential for the formation of chemical bonds, without which life would not be possible. Upgrade the Nano-Bot-Cell molecule harvester and immune defense system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Sometimes having resources isn't everything!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Having to perfectly combine a long sequence of chemical elements is not easy to memorize or reproduce, but necessary for the prosperity of the colony.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Bonus events:</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get more extra 'coins' to increase your skills with random mini-games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>SynthetiCell BioClicker demonstrates how simple systems can generate surprising complexity, inspiring new research and applications in many fields.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/5f9f42a22519a319e4b580700d2a6f93.poster.avif?t=1745050479\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/5f9f42a22519a319e4b580700d2a6f93.webm?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/5f9f42a225